post_text:
April 27, 2018
Dear Members of the Winchendon Public Schools Community:
At the Wednesday, April 25, 2018 school committee meeting the members approved the appointment of Rich Ikonen as “Acting Superintendent” pending the return of Superintendent Steven Haddad. This move was necessary for clarity as to who is in charge in the district while Mr. Haddad remains on leave. All duties, decision-making powers, and responsibilities of the office will be afforded Mr. Ikonen while Acting Superintendent. Questions and/or concerns should be directed to Rich and no one should contact Mr. Haddad until further notice. Mr. Ikonen is working on a plan to ensure his business manager responsibilities will not… More
